    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus domini <persName key="#Popes"
                            ref="#people/1584">Iohannis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">pape</rs> sedis secundi, <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperatore</rs> nondum habemus, die vigesimo quarto mensis octuber,
                        indictione nona, <placeName ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>. Petimus a
                        vobis in Dei nomine domnus <persName key="#Priests #Abbots #Monks"
                            ref="#people/1574">Vuido</persName> gratia Dei <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monacus</rs> atque <rs key="#Abbots"
                            >abbatis</rs> regule venerabilis <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mountains #Landed_possessions #Forests #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wood #Cows #Pigs #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Books #Canals #Levies#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie que vocatur a <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Monasteries" ref="#places/4179"
                                >Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, una cum consensum deservientium
                        eidem regule, uti nobis in Dei nomine <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus/de Vitalis">Petrus qui vocatur de
                            Vitalis</name></persName> petitore pro me et pro <persName><name
                                ref="Christina">Cristina</name></persName> iugalis mea seu filiis
                        nostris <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">livellario</rs> nomine
                        concedisti nobis rem iuris predicti monasterii vestri, idest <rs key="#Size"
                            >quadraginta quatuor turnature</rs> inter <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Production">terra laboratoria</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Forests">silva</rs>, que sunt posite in locum qui vocatur
                            <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mountains #Landed_possessions #Forests #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wood #Cows #Pigs #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Books #Canals #Levies"
                            ref="#places/4606">Campo Domnico</placeName>, sitas <rs key="#Fines"
                            >territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/3513"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/2424">Faventino</geogName></placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebis</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1490">Sancti Iohannis qui
                            vocatur in <placeName ref="#places/3527">Axilata</placeName></orgName>;
                        abendam, tenendam, cultandam, laborandam, <rs key="#Wine">vineam</rs> inibi
                        implatitandam, supersedendum, defensandum et in omnibus meliorandum, in
                        annis avenientibus viginti et novem at renovandum, salva sanatione domnico
                        dandum. Ita sane ut inferamus domnice rationibus singulis quibusque annis oc
                        est <rs key="#Levies">terratico</rs>: de omni <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >labore maiore</rs> modio quinto et de omni quinta <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">minuto</rs> modio sex, cum vino amfora tertia,
                        post vineam incollome deducta fuerit, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >arbore</rs> pecto ponente duas vice piciolo semel inciso, relico sit
                        nobis concesso; aducto et omnia terratico usque in <rs key="#Cities"
                            >civitatem</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>, in domo de
                        monasterii vestri; et omnique anno dare vobis debeamus de <rs key="#Cows"
                            >bubus</rs> paria huna cum carro a vecturia mittendum da <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montanea</rs> si bubus abuerimus et si bubus non
                        abuerimus at manibus aciuvare debeamus et omnique anno aciuvare debeamus ac
                            <rs key="#Wood">lignario</rs> vestro domnico ponendum diebus octo cum
                        uno pario de bobus et cum carro si abuerimus et si non abuerimus at manibus
                        aciuvare debeamus et omnique anno dare vobis debeamus <rs key="#Pigs"
                            >porco</rs> uno et omnique anno in asumtione Marie dare vobis debeamus
                        medietatem de uno <rs>ferserigo</rs>; et non abeamus licentia trictulare nec
                        vindimiare sine iuridictione hominum vestrorum vel vestra dominatione cum
                        onore et obedientia susipere debeamus et subseptione ei facere et
                            <rs>brachiaticam</rs> ei persolvere de labore et de vino omnique anno de
                        omni <rs key="#Canals">canale</rs> starias duodecim, cum fide et puritate
                        seu humilitate, sine dolo vel fraude aut malo ingenio. Pro quia recepimus
                        calciarii, idest <rs key="#Books">libro</rs> uno <rs key="#Price">pro
                            denariorum Venetorum de ... solidos quadraginta</rs>. Et vos dictus
                        abbas cum tuis successoribus stare et autoriare seu defensare debeatis. Si
                        quis vero pars vestra contra hac petitione temtaveritis antequam finitum
                        tempus, det pars parti ante omnes litis initium aut interpellationem pene
                        nomine <rs key="#Penalty">auri uncias duas</rs> et post pene solutionem anc
                        petitio in sua firmitate. <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabellio</rs> Ravennas scribendum rogavi unus alterius, sup die et
                        mense et indictione nona, Ravenne. Signum manus Petrus qui vocatur de
                        Vitalis petitore at omnia supradicta cui relectum est.</ab>
                </div>
